           \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\n  \u001b[38;5;252m5. Gradually beat in flour mixture.                                                             \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\n  \u001b[38;5;252m6. Stir in chocolate morsels and nuts.                                                          \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\n  \u001b[38;5;252m7. Drop by rounded tablespoon onto ungreased baking sheets.                                     \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\n  \u001b[38;5;252m8. Bake for 9 to 11 minutes or until golden brown.                              "]
